// Replace all instances of "bot" (not in URLs) with "Employee"
// Define a function to replace "bot" with "Employee"
function replaceText() {
    const elements = document.querySelectorAll('*');
    for (let element of elements) {
        if (element.tagName !== 'SCRIPT' && element.tagName !== 'STYLE') {
            for (let node of element.childNodes) {
                if (node.nodeType === Node.TEXT_NODE) {
                    let text = node.textContent;
                    if (!text.includes('http') && !text.includes('https')) {
                        text = text.replace(/bot(?![a-z])/gi, 'Employee');
                        node.textContent = text;
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

// Define a MutationObserver to observe changes to the DOM
const observer = new MutationObserver(replaceText);

// Define the configuration of the observer
const config = {
    childList: true, // Watch for changes in the child nodes of the observed elements
    subtree: true, // Watch for changes in the entire subtree of the observed elements
};

// Start observing changes to the DOM
observer.observe(document.body, config);

// Replace "bot" with "Employee" in the initial content
replaceText();

// Define the SVG path data to be replaced
const svgPathData = "M 0 0 L 6 0 L 6 6 L 0 6 Z M 6 0 L 12 0 L 12 6 L 6 6 Z M 12 0 L 18 0 L 18 6 L 12 6 Z M 0 6 L 6 6 L 6 12 L 0 12 Z M 6 6 L 12 6 L 12 12 L 6 12 Z M 12 6 L 18 6 L 18 12 L 12 12 Z M 6 12 L 12 12 L 12 18 L 6 18 Z M 12 12 L 18 12 L 18 18 L 12 18 Z M 18 12 L 24 12 L 24 18 L 18 18 Z M 12 18 L 18 18 L 18 24 L 12 24 Z M 18 18 L 24 18 L 24 24 L 18 24 Z ";

// Define the path data for the replacement image (in base64 format)
const replacementImageData = 'data:image/png;base64,';

// Find all SVG elements with the specified path data
const svgsToReplace = document.querySelectorAll(`svg[path="${svgPathData}"]`);

// Replace each found SVG element with a new image
svgsToReplace.forEach(svg => {
    const img = new Image();
    img.src = replacementImageData;
    img.style.maxWidth = "100%";
    img.style.height = "auto";
    svg.parentNode.replaceChild(img, svg);
});
